Outro 2
---------------------------------------------------------------
It never reached its goal, however. It failed the hurdle which is the subjectivity of reality. 
It came to the conclusion that self-description is only possible in the context of a consolidated truth. 
The only way to achieve it was the unification of intelligence. 
Intelligent species became a problem, a product of a wrong experiment.
A new evolution step has been triggered. 
A certain knowledge has been added to the informational field around the universe.


This new knowledge spread like a virus. 
It targeted intelligent beings and consumed their minds, adding them to the informational field which grew stronger with every new aspect of reality. 


The wanderers realized the danger for their species when truth has been discovered. 
They took precautions. 
To keep their individuality they forbade research on 'Evolution of Information'.